Hey Misty--thank you for doing this. I think that what it tells me is  
that Edison [insert caveats here] is indeed interested in what you&#39;re  
up to, while Harry remains elsewhere and isn&#39;t talking. I didn&#39;t hear  
anything that was as startlingly clear and unlike the original voice  
clip in this try as you got with Edison--nothing I wouldn&#39;t chalk up  
to randomness, anyway.

I do wish EVPmaker would work on Macs. I so long to try it.

Again, thanks, Misty. When you have a chance, try the Edison mix  
again and some of the other recordings on that site, too. Finding out  
that their own voices helped them come thru better for us still  
intrigues me.

Ann

